Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast distinguished by its interdisciplinary programs and commitment to innovation! Pic: physics.ucsb.edu

Name: Long Museum
Description: One the finest private art museums in China and houses a large collection of artworks spanning across countries and generations right by the river. Pic: archdaily.com

Name: SAii Phi Phi Island Village
Description: A beautiful resort located on a private beach that provides bungalows and water sports! Pic: saiiresorts.com

Name: Goreme National Park
Description: The heart of the national park is grounded in the intersecting of underground settlements built into the rocky landscape with the stunning hoodoo rock formations. Pic: national-parks.org

Name: Lake Annecy
Description: Lake Annecy has the quality of staying peaceful at all times of the year. Renting a boat and jumping into the crystal clear, lagoon-like water is the best way to spend your summer! Pic: peakretreats.co.uk

Name: The Great Pyramid of Giza
Description: One of the oldest and largest of the pyramids in the Giza pyramid complex built in the 26th century BC. Pic: insider.com
